title: My First Post, Yo!
author: Kyu Seok Yeum
content: Welcome to My Blog. *It's a beautiful thing.* I hope you'll have as much fun reading my posts as I have writing them. Well, before we go any further, allow em to introduce myself. I'm Kyu and I'm 24, living in Sout Korea.
